as i hate being the third wheel and i was never or never felt like the third wheel around my friends girlfriends or stuff like that, it comes as no surprise that i am the third wheel around my own gf and her best friend,&nbsp;&nbsp; she might as well be her bf they get along better&nbsp; anyway,&nbsp; she makes her laugh something that i have a hard enough time doing even though i spend every day with her. it doesnt seem to matter, when she is around i might as well not exist,&nbsp; i try to talk and i talked over,&nbsp; its like my life i try to live and i get walked over. i get used&nbsp; im a doormat a step for people to whipe their feet on&nbsp; welcoming them into something better. im just the piece of shit you wipe all the dirt off before u take your shoes off and go walk on the real nice carpet and relax.&nbsp; just apparently im one welcome mat that doesnt want to let my victim go.&nbsp;even though the carpet is calling out to her.&nbsp; although&nbsp; its by choice hopefully that she stays.&nbsp; im really jealous of her best friend because i cant do that to her. make her laugh , make her happy&nbsp; get along so well, share all the inside jokes of years.&nbsp; i guess im my own enemy on this one, no one can help me make her laugh at my stupid jokes, no one can make her get along with me 100% of the time.&nbsp; but i keep trying to make it work and i feel its like&nbsp; trying to keep up a house of cards as its falling down. impossible.&nbsp; but i love her and she yells at me all the time.&nbsp; and i cry and she&nbsp; hugs me and makes me feel better ..... occasionally.&nbsp; i was playing gamecube while she was cooking&nbsp; and waiting for her friend. so when she asked me to stop i was fine with that. but i had to save it&nbsp; and i knew i didnt have enough time&nbsp; to get to the savepoint so i turned off the t.v.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; as to be able to save it later when i had time to.&nbsp; but she was just mad i played at all.&nbsp;&nbsp; but when she decides to play i sit and watch intently because&nbsp; i dont mind.&nbsp;&nbsp; but she wont&nbsp; watch me play nor will she ever its interesting as long as its one game and she is playing, mind you she doesnt mind when i play the 1 game&nbsp; that she likes, but&nbsp; as soon as its any other game, she doesnt want me to play it unless im home, which 1) i want to be with her and 2) i dont want to be home.&nbsp;


its almost as if she tries to not pay attention to me at times.&nbsp;
she tried to send me home, and really i dont want to&nbsp; because one she wanted me to be there and two i wanted to be there.
i wish i was her, to be so care free and loving and connected at the same time, not jealous and full of stupidity,&nbsp;
cut me down
bring me down to whatever you want to me just give me that connection, i would give anything to be as close to her as her best friend.
i love her so much and i wish things were as good with us as it is with her and her friend.






















